# RTOS ready-queue priority pick (highest prio = lowest number).
*pick(prios as Vec of i64, n as i64) returns i64
    idx is 0
    best is prios.get(0)
    i is 1
    while i < n
        if prios.get(i) < best
            best is prios.get(i)
            idx is i
        i is i + 1
    idx

*main
    p is vec()
    p.push(5)
    p.push(2)
    p.push(7)
    p.push(1)
    p.push(3)
    log pick(p, 5)
